Coronavirus na yau da kullun da ke haifar da cutar (COVID-19) a Tarayyar Turai / Hukumar Tsaro ta Turai da Majalisar Ingila, 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
A halin yanzu, cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ta nuna alamun cutar a cikin ƙasashen Turai da Turai da kuma Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, yayin da a wani lokaci, cutar COVID-19 ta kasance cikin gaggawa a cikin ƙasashen duniya.
Idan muka yi la'akari da abin da ke faruwa a Italiya, jihohi, asibitoci da kungiyoyin kulawa da marasa lafiya za su buƙaci su ƙara yin shiri don yawan mutanen da ke da COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman, da kuma yawan kulawa.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, wani rukunin masu cutar kansa na musamman da ba a san sunayensu ba ya bayyana a Wuhan, Lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Hukumar Kula da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta sanar da cewa ba za a iya gano sabon coronavirus ba, wanda aka kira shi da coronavirus na numfashi na 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da SARS-CoV ya haifar ana kiranta cuta (COVI-19).
Rahotanni na baya sun ce kusan kashi 80% na mutanen da ke fama da cutar na da mummunar illa, kamar cututtukan huhu, da kuma ciwon sukari.
A cikin kashi 14% na masu kamuwa da COVID-19, an ba su magani mai kyau da kuma asibiti, kuma a cikin kashi 6% na masu kamuwa da cutar, an ba su magani mai kyau da kuma kula da likita.
Mutuwar marasa lafiya a asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kashi 4 cikin dari.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun bincika yanayin COVID-19 a kowace ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai / Tarayyar Turai (EU/EEA) da kuma Majalisar ofishin Burtaniya (UK) yayin da mai magana da yawun ke lardin Hubei, China.
Hakanan zan iya kwatanta adadin masu cutar COVID-19 na yanzu a cikin EU/EEA da UK tare da waɗanda ke Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
COVID-19 ya ɓarke a cikin EU/EEA da UK
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya yaɗu zuwa wasu ƙasashe kuma ɓarkewar cutar COVID-19 a wasu ƙasashe na duniya yanzu yana da tasiri a kan wannan ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin rahoton Eurosurveillance na ranar 5 ga Maris, 2020, Spiteri et al. ya ba da rahoton farkon cutar COVID-19 a Turai bisa ga WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta ba da rahoton mutum uku da suka kamu da cutar a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da United Kingdom, inda aka samu mutane 39,768 da suka kamu da cutar da kuma 1,727 da suka mutu a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, da kuma 1,441 a Italiya.
Ƙungiyar ta yi kira ga ƙungiyar masu cutar COVID-19
A cikin Hukumar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), an sabunta adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda ya danganta da masu ba da shawara kamar Ma'aikatar Kiwon Lafiya ta Duniya, hukumomin kula da lafiya na jihohi da birane da WHO da kuma bayanan da aka samu a ranar Talata da misalin karfe 8:00 na safe.
Ana amfani da wannan bayanan don gwajin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da kuma a cikin UK, tare da yin amfani da shi don gwadawa da Italiya.
A matsayin nazarin yanayin cutar COVID-19, mun tattara tarin cututtukan COVID-19 na asali, amma mun kuma tattara adadin COVID-19 a kowace EU/EEA da UK daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Mun kuma kawo jimlar adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar a kowace kasa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8:00 na safe a kasar Italiya daga ranar 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
COVID-19 ya bullo ne a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya.
A cikin jerin jerin abubuwan da aka samu na yawan masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA a cikin kwanaki 14 da suka gabata, an bi mafi yawan Burtaniya da lardin Hubei na China (Hoto na 1).
Dangane da EU/EEA da UK, jimlar adadin masu cutar COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu kuma ya ragu zuwa 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (Bayanin).
Babban abin da ya kawo wannan damuwa shi ne cewa ba a kai yawan adadin masu cutar ba a Italiya, yayin da sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya ke nuna irin wannan ci gaba a cikin adadin masu cutar COVID-19 (Bayanin).
Hoto na 2 ya nuna jimillar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19, a cikin EU/EEA da UK idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya a lokacin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
A lura cewa, a ranar 15 ga Maris da karfe 8:00 na dare, ƙasashe 15 na EU/EEA da kuma wasu UK sun ba da sanarwar adadin mutanen da za su iya kamuwa da cutar a Italiya a cikin makonni 3 kafin ko bayan ranar ƙarshe.
Wannan ya nuna cewa adadin adadin COVID-19 da aka ruwaito bai yi daidai ba a cikin EU/EEA da UK.
Halin da muke ciki na COVID-19 ya nuna cewa cutar ta riga ta kamu da cutar da za ta iya haifar da cutar a ƙasashen duniya.
Wannan ya faru ne saboda ƙasashe da ke da bambancin ra'ayi, canje-canje a cikin tsarin kula da lafiya na ƙasa, da kuma bambancin bayyanar cutar a ƙasashe da sauran hanyoyin da za a iya tantance waɗanda suka buƙaci a sake duba su don COVID-19, da kuma sake gwada su.
A farkon Maris 2020, likitocin a cikin yankuna da ke fama da cutar Italiya sun gano cewa kusan kashi 10% na masu cutar COVID-19 suna buƙatar kulawa ta musamman kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ce asibitoci da ƙungiyoyin kulawa na musamman a waɗannan yankuna sun ba da ƙarin bayani.
Bayanai kan COVID-19 a asibitoci da/ko kungiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya sun kasance a cikin EU/EEA na 6% da 1% na masu kamuwa da cutar, da sauransu (a cikin bayanan da aka nuna).
Bayan haka, za su haɗa su a cikin shafi ɗaya don samar da bayanai game da kula da dabbobin da aka gano da kuma mutuwar.
