Kwayar cutar coronavirus ta mutum ta hanyar dabbobi
Kwayar cuta da ke haifar da cutar coronavirus (CoV) ta kasance mai yaduwa da kuma karɓa daga wasu mutane, a cikin shekaru da yawa.
Kafin 2003, an gano wasu CoVs na mutum (HCoVs) guda biyu da suka haifar da cututtukan cututtuka, kamar su mura.
Cututtuka kamar su SARS da MERS sun nuna yadda cutar ke shafar mutane.
Bayan ɓarkewar SARS-CoV-2 a tsakiyar China a ƙarshen 2019 ya kamu da cutar CoV da kuma haifar da mummunar cuta mai saurin kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin ƙwayoyin cuta.
HCoVs na da ƙwayoyin cuta kuma gano asalin ƙwayoyin cuta na HCoVs na iya zama da amfani a gare mu.
Yawancin HCoVs sun fito ne daga kwari kuma ba su da wata cuta.
An kuma gano wasu kwayoyin HCoV masu matsakaicin matsayi.
Koyon dabbobi masu kama da gidaje yana da matukar muhimmanci wajen koyon yadda mutum zai iya kare kansa.
