Makarantun da ke kewayen Seattle sun dakatar da karatu a ranar 3 ga Maris, kuma tun daga tsakiyar Maris, makarantu a cikin ƙasar za su rufe makarantu.A ranar 6 ga Maris, an ba da sanarwar cewa Amurka na fuskantar sabon kamuwa da kwayar cutar coronavirus a cikin gida ta hanyar ƙungiyar masu binciken cutar a Imperial College London.
A ranar Talata, Shugaba Trump ya ba da umarnin dokar Coronavirus Preparedness and Response Supplemental Appropriations Act, wanda ya ba da dala biliyan 8.3 a matsayin taimakon gaggawa ga cibiyoyin gwamnati don amsa cutar.
Kamfanoni sun ba da umarnin tafiye-tafiye ga ma'aikatansu, sun hana tarurruka, kuma sun hana ma'aikata yin aiki daga gida.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, Trump ya sanar da dakatar da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama zuwa ga mafi yawan kasashen Turai, ban da Birtaniya, na tsawon kwanaki 30, daga ranar 13 ga Maris.
A cikin shekara ta gaba, ya fadada wannan ra'ayi a Ingila da Ireland.
A ranar 13 ga Maris, an sanar da gaggawa na kasa, wanda ya haifar da kudaden da aka adana a cikin asusun tallafi don amsawa.
Tun daga ranar 15 ga Maris, yawancin kamfanoni a Amurka sun rufe ko kuma sun sake yin jirage a wani mataki na rage yaduwar cutar.
A ranar 17 ga watan Maris, an samu rahotannin cutar a jihohi 50 da kuma cikin Columbia. A ranar 23 ga watan Maris, an ruwaito cewa birnin New York yana da mutum 10,700 da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus, wanda ya fi na Koriya ta Kudu.
A ranar 5 ga Maris, gwamnati ta ce dokar hana fita ta yi tasiri, kuma adadin mutanen da ke da lafiya ya ragu daga kwanaki 2.0 zuwa 4.7.
