A cewar wani rahoto da aka bayar a ranar 30 ga watan Maris, Shugaba Trump na Amurka ya yi niyyar tsawaita dokar hana fita daga kasar har zuwa ranar 30 ga watan Afrilu.
A cikin wannan, USNS Comfort, wani asibiti mai girman gado da ke da asibiti mai ɗauke da gado 1,000, ya tsaya a New York.
A ranar 3 ga watan Afrilu, Amurka ta yi kiyasin mutuwar mutum 884 da suka mutu sakamakon cutar korona a cikin kwanaki 24.
A jihar New York an kiyasta adadin masu kamuwa da cutar ya zarce 100,000 a ranar 3 ga Afrilu.Fadar White House ta gano cewa cutar ta haifar da cutar kuma tana sa ido kan al'amuran ta hanyar tura jami'an kiwon lafiya da masana don ba da shawara ga al'ummomin da ke fuskantar al'amuran da suka shafi cutar da kuma al'amuran da suka shafi shugaban kasa Mike Pence na biyu.
Duk da haka, Trump ya yi amfani da wasu hanyoyin da mutane ke ganin sun yi tasiri a kan cutar.
Wasu shugabannin Amurka da masu yawon bude ido sun soki Amurka saboda rashin amincewa da kayayyakin da ba su da daraja a kasashen waje, kamar maganin gargajiya, a China.
Wani bincike kan iskar gas da aka dauka don tantancewa da kuma tantance yadda iskar ke sauka ya fito ne a Journal of Travel Medicine a tsakiyar watan Janairun 2020.
A cewar wani rahoto na shekara ta 2018 daga kungiyar sufurin jiragen sama ta kasa da kasa, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo, da Taipei sun fi yawan wadanda suka yi tafiya daga Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney, da Melbourne sun kuma bayyana a matsayin wuraren da ake samun karuwar matafiya daga Wuhan.
Bali an bayar da rahoton a matsayin mafi ƙarancin yawon shakatawa a cikin birane 20 da suka fi yawan yawon buɗe ido ko yawon shakatawa, yayin da birane a Ostiraliya suka fi yawan balaguro. Ostiraliya ta ba da sanarwar Karin Magani game da Coronavirus (COVID-19) a ranar 7 ga Fabrairu.
An ba da ƙarin haske game da cutar COVID-19, kuma Ostiraliya za ta ƙara ƙuntatawa da kuma nuna bambanci a cikin martanin da ta bayar game da cutar.
A ranar 21 ga Maris, an yi gargadin gaggawa game da cutar shan inna a Ostiraliya.
Don magance matsalar rashin lafiyar da ke tattare da cutar a Wuhan da Hubei, ƙasashe da yawa sun shirya don kwashe 'yan ƙasarsu da jami'an tsaro daga yankin, da farko ta jirgin sama da ke da alhakin kai tsaye, tare da taimakon gwamnatin China.
