An yi gwajin lafiya kafin a yi rigakafin, kuma duk wani mutumin Afirka ta Kudu da ke da alamun cutar coronavirus ya kamata a yi shi nan da nan don rage kamuwa da cutar.
Ba a maida mazauna Afirka ta Kudu da suka kamu da cutar ba a matsayin 'yan kasarsu.
Rahoton ya nuna cewa dukkan 'yan kasar Afirka ta Kudu, ciki har da hukumar kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama, ma'aikatan jirgin sama, masu kula da otel, 'yan sanda da kuma sojoji masu ba da agaji, sun kasance a karkashin tsare-tsare kuma sun kasance ba su da izinin shiga cikin kwanaki 14 a Ranch Resort.
A ranar 20 ga Maris, Amurka ta fara janye dakarunta daga Iraki saboda cutar.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Ofishin Jakadancin China ya sanar da cewa kasashe 21 (har da Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad da Tobago, Masar, da Iran) sun ba da tallafi ga kasar Sin.
Wasu ma'aikatan likitancin kasar Sin a cibiyoyin kiwon lafiya na Amurka sun yi kira da a tura taimako zuwa yankunan da cutar ta shafa a China, tare da wasu kungiyoyi a yankin Chicago da ke da iyaka wadanda suka yi gwagwarmaya don ba da kyautar N95 50,000 ga wasu asibitocin lardin Hubei a ranar 30 ga Janairu.Kungiyar ba da agaji ta Direct Relief, tare da taimakon FedEx, ta tura kayan rufe fuska 200,000 da sauran kayayyaki, kamar kayan aikin hannu da kayan aiki, ta jirgin saman gaggawa zuwa Wuhan Union Hospital a ranar 30 ga Janairu.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Bill da Melinda Gates sun ba da sanarwar bayar da tallafin dala miliyan 100 ga WHO don binciken magungunan cutar da kuma hanyoyin magance ta da kuma hana "ƙananan ƙasashe na Afirka da Kudancin Asiya kamuwa da cutar".
An ba da rahoton cewa gwamnatin China ta ba da kyautar abin rufe fuska 200,000 ga Filipinos a ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, bayan da Sanata Richard Gordon ya ba da kyautar abin rufe fuska miliyan 3.16 a Wuhan.
A ranar 19 ga Fabrairu, Ƙungiyar agaji ta Singapore ta sanar da cewa za ta aika da dala miliyan 2.26 domin taimaka wa ƙasar Sin.
Japan ta ba da rigunan rigakafi a Wuhan, Turkiyya ta ba da umarnin asibiti, Rasha ta ba da kayan aikin likita da kayan aiki sama da tan 13 a Wuhan, Malaysia ta ba da rahoton ba da kayan aikin hannu miliyan 18 ga China, Jamus ta ba da kayan aikin likita da kayan aikin kiwon lafiya 10,000, kuma Amurka ta ba da asibiti da kayan aikin likita tan 17.8 ga China kuma ta ba da ƙarin dala miliyan 100 a matsayin tallafi da kuɗi ga ƙasashe masu tasowa.Bayan an ba da rahoton cewa cutar ta ragu a China, kasar ta fara ba da tallafi ga sauran ƙasashe da ke fama da cutar.
A watan Maris, China, Cuba da Rasha sun aika da kayan aikin likita da likitoci don taimakawa Italiya yaƙi da annobar coronavirus.
Kamfanin Jack Ma ya aika da umarni na gwaji miliyan 1.1, da takardar rufe baki miliyan 6, da takardar rufe baki 60,000 zuwa Addis Ababa, Habasha don rarraba ta Ƙungiyar Tarayyar Afirka.
Daga baya ya aika kayan gwaje-gwaje 5,000, rigunan rufe fuska 100,000 da kuma jirgin saman jirgin sama 5 zuwa Panama.
Haka kuma, an ba da kyautar kayayyakin kiwon lafiya ga kasar Canada. Netherlands, Spain, Turkey, Georgia, da Czech Republic sun nuna damuwa game da rigakafin rigakafin da aka yi a China da kuma kayayyakin gwaji.
Misali, Spain ta fitar da kayan gwajin cutar Sin 58 000 wadanda suka nuna ingancin cutar ta 30%, yayin da Netherlands ta fitar da kayan aikin kashe gobara na kasar Sin 600 000 wadanda suka nuna ingancin cutar.
Belgium ta yi watsi da takunkumin rufe fuska 100,000, bayan da aka gano cewa sun fito ne daga Colombia.
A wani lokaci, an ba da taimakon taimakon agaji na kasar Sin a wasu yankuna na Latin Amurka da Afirka.A ranar 2 ga Afrilu, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta kaddamar da ayyukan agaji na gaggawa ga kasashen da ke fama da talauci.
Hukumar ta WHO ta yi tir da kokarin da gwamnatin kasar Sin ke yi na hana yaduwar cutar.
WHO ta lura da bambanci tsakanin barkewar cutar SARS a 2002-2004, wadda aka zargi gwamnatin China da aikata ta'asa da kuma rashin bin ka'idojin hana yaduwa da kuma dakile cutar, da kuma barkewar cutar da gwamnatin China ta "ba da rahoton mutane uku da suka kamu da cutar kafin a fara sabuwar shekara".
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, a cikin martani ga kiran da gwamnatin tsakiya ta yi na hana barazanar cutar a Wuhan, wakilin WHO Gauden Galea ya ce "ba a taba samun wani mataki na WHO ba", yana mai cewa "yana da muhimmanci gwamnati ta yi kokari wajen hana wannan annoba daga barkewa a cikin wani lokaci mafi muni" kuma ya ce "ba a taba samun irin wannan a tarihin kiwon lafiya ba". A ranar 30 ga watan Janairu, bayan an tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar daga mutum zuwa mutum a wajen kasar Sin da kuma samun karuwar masu kamuwa da cutar a wasu ƙasashe, WHO ta sanar da cewa cutar ta kamu da cutar ta cutar ta duniya (PHEIC), kuma ita ce ta farko da PHEIC ta yi tun bayan da aka fara gudanar da shirin kamuwa da cutar a shekarar 2009.
Babban sakataren WHO Tedros Adhanom ya ce cutar PHEIC na iya "zama da saurin yaduwa a duniya, musamman a kasashe masu karancin lafiya da ke da karancin hanyoyin kiwon lafiya masu inganci".
Dangane da koma bayan da aka samu a kan tafiye-tafiye, Tedros ya ce "babu wani canji ga matakan da ke hana tafiye-tafiye zuwa wasu ƙasashe da kasuwanci" kuma "WHO ta ba da shawarar rage kasuwanci ko rashin lafiya".
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairun, WHO ta yi kira ga al'umman duniya da su yi amfani da matakan da suka dace don samar da tallafin da ya kai dala miliyan 675 ga ƙasashe masu ƙarancin ci gaba, ta hanyar yin kira ga ƙasashen da "ba su da tsarin kula da lafiyar jama'a, ko da kuwa sun shiga cikin wani yanayi na rashin lafiya".
Tedros ya kara da cewa "mu masu karfi ne kamar kashin jikinmu" kuma ya yi kira ga al'ummar duniya da su "yi kokarin magance wannan cuta yanzu ko kuma a kara tsanantawa nan gaba".A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, WHO a taron manema labarai ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin cutar.
A wannan ranar, Tedros ya ce Babban Sakataren Majalisar Dinkin Duniya António Guterres ya amince da "dakatar da duk wata manufa ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a cikin wannan martani".
Ƙungiyar ta Majalisar Ɗinkin Duniya ta World Health Organization ta ba da amsa, ta ba da umarni ga Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wadda WHO ta ba da shawara cewa "a ba da shawara ga al'umma a kan lafiyar lafiyar jama'a a lokaci guda, kuma sauran kungiyoyi za su iya yin amfani da su don magance matsalolin da suka shafi al'umma, da kuma al'ummominmu".
A ranar 14 ga watan Fabrairu, Hukumar Kula da Kula da Kula da Kula da China ta yi kira ga wakilan kasashen waje da na WHO a China da su taimaka wajen yin bincike da kuma gano "aukuwar cutar da kuma yadda za a iya yada ta" a cikin kasar ta hanyar tuntuɓar manyan cibiyoyin bincike da cibiyoyin bincike na kasashen waje don "ƙaddamar da ayyukan da za a yi a lardin da ƙauyuka, birane da garuruwa". A ranar 25 ga watan Fabrairu, WHO ta ce "a yanzu duniya tana yin shirye-shiryen da za a yi game da yiwuwar kamuwa da cutar coronavirus", kuma ta sanar da cewa a cikin wani lokaci za a iya gano da kuma kawar da cutar, kuma dole ne ƙasashe su kasance "a matakin farko".
A sakamakon sakamakon cutar da ke ci gaba a Iran, WHO ta tura wani rukunin bincike na musamman don yin bincike kan cutar.A ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, jami'an WHO sun ce za a fara gudanar da binciken cutar coronavirus a duniya daga "babban" zuwa "ƙananan", wanda zai zama matakin ƙarshe na binciken cutar.
Mike Ryan, mai kula da shirin gaggawa na kiwon lafiya na WHO, ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa cewa "Wannan ya zama babban abin mamaki ga kowace gwamnati a duniya: Muna da lafiya.
Wannan kwayar cutar za ta iya zama mai zaman kanta kuma dole ne a kawar da ita", ta hanyar samar da hanyoyin da za a iya samun mafita wanda zai iya hana duniya "ta hanyar yin amfani da ita".
Ryan ya kuma kara da cewa wannan bayanai na yanzu zai ba da tabbaci ga jami'an kiwon lafiya game da yadda cutar ta barke, yana mai cewa sakamakon ya nuna cewa "muna da babban tabbaci cewa kowane mutum a duniya zai iya kamuwa da cutar".
A watan Maris, WHO ta ayyana coronavirus a matsayin annoba.
Babban Daraktan ya ce WHO ta "ƙware sosai kan lamuran cutar da kuma yadda cutar ke yaduwa, da kuma yadda ake samun ci gaba". WHO ta yi la'akari da muhimmancin da ke tattare da abubuwan da ke faruwa a duniya kamar yadda ake kula da cutar, da kuma muhimmancin da ke tattare da al'amuran da suka shafi lafiyar jama'a da kuma shigar da cutar a cikin kungiyoyin cutar.
Har ila yau, an yi watsi da sanarwar da aka ba wa Shugaban WHO Tedros Adhanom na dakatar da aikinsa, wanda mutane 733,000 suka sanya hannu a ranar 6 ga Afrilu.
A ranar 26 ga Maris, 2020, Kwamitin Kula da Lafiya na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya yi wa'adi kan wasu shawarwari 10 da za a yi don ci gaba da kula da lafiyar dan Adam a yayin annobar COVID-19.
Kungiyar ta ce duk abin da aka yi ya shafi shirin satar mutane, kuma gwamnati na da hannu a ciki.
Ƙungiyar ta yi jayayya cewa rashin samun tsarin kiwon lafiya mai inganci ba zai iya zama hanyar warkar da sauran jama'a ba.
Masu bincike sun kuma yi la'akari da duk wanda ke da matsalar rashin lafiya, ciki har da mutanen da ke da cututtukan haihuwa, da kuma wadanda ke cikin kungiyoyi masu zaman kansu, da tsofaffi, da mutanen da suka yi canje-canje a rayuwarsu a kasar, da marasa gida, da marasa lafiya, da fursunoni, da masu neman taimako da sauran kungiyoyin da ke bukatar taimakon gwamnati.
Hukumomin duniya suna ta gwagwarmaya don magance matsalolin tattalin arziki da zamantakewa da COVID-19 ya haifar.
Kwamitin Ci Gaban Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya ba da tabbacin bayar da bayanai a kan lokaci game da manufofin siyasa na ƙasashen duniya, da kuma abubuwan da suka shafi siyasa.
Daga manufofin da suka shafi kiwon lafiya da tsaro na duniya zuwa rage yawan zaman gida da kuma rage zirga-zirgar ababen hawa, daga cikin manufofin da suka shafi harkokin waje na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, ya haɗa da ƙoƙarin taimakawa ƙasashe su koyi yadda za su yi aiki da kuma shirya don sake fashewa na coronavirus.
