Gwamnan Amurka Donald Trump ya yi watsi da coronavirus a matsayin "kwayar cutar China" ko "kwayar cutar Wuhan" kuma ya ce China "ta gano wata cuta da ta zama annoba a yanzu", wanda wasu masu sukar suka yi da'awar cewa ba ta da tushe kuma "ba za a iya zargi hukuma ba saboda rashin kulawar da ta yi".
The Daily Beast ta sami wata sanarwa daga gwamnatin Amurka da ke nuna irin yadda ake samun ta'aziyyar da aka samu daga Kwamitin Tsaro na Kasa, kuma an kira wannan shirin "Duk abin da ya shafi kasar Sin.
An kuma bayyana cewa za a iya yin la'akari da irin wannan tallafi a wasu hanyoyi, ciki har da a kafofin watsa labarai da kuma a shafukan yanar gizo".Kasuwancin kasuwanci kamar Politico, Foreign Policy, da Bloomberg sun nuna cewa duk wani yunƙurin da China ke yi na neman tallafin ƙasashen waje na nuna rashin amincewa da ƙasashen duniya.
Shugaban harkokin wajen Josep Borrell ya ce akwai "wani tsarin siyasa da ke ci gaba da kasancewa a nan gaba a matsayin wata hanya ta samun ci gaba ta hanyar siyasa da kuma "samar da taimako".
