Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) yana da dogon lokaci yana wanzuwa a cikin ƙwayoyin cuta (duba ƙwayoyin cuta) a cikin huhu, jini, zuciya, tsoka, da kuma jijiyoyin jiki.
ACE2 yana hana aikin angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) ta hanyar rage yawan angiotensin-II da kuma ƙara Ang ((1-7) wanda ya sa ya zama magani mai mahimmanci a cikin maganin cututtukan zuciya. ACE2 kuma yana aiki a matsayin ƙofar shiga cikin ƙwayoyin cuta na wasu coronaviruses.
Kwayar halittar ɗan adam ana kiranta HACE2.
Angiotensin converting enzyme 2 shi ne zinc-containing metalloenzyme kuma yana samuwa a cikin endothelial da sauran kwayoyin halitta.
ACE2 yana da yankin N-terminal peptidase M2 da kuma C-terminal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 shine wani nau'in furotin mai suna type I membrane, wanda ke dauke da sinadarin dake aiki a jikin jikin kwayoyin halitta da kuma sauran kwayoyin halitta.
ACE2 yankin a waje na cell an haɗa shi da wani yankin transmembrane ta hanyar wani fili mai suna sheddase, kuma sunadarai masu gina jiki suna shiga cikin jini kuma a ƙarshe sun fita daga cikin mahaifa.
